Package: localmaximas
Type: Package
Title: Identifies locally maximal points in a Canopy Height Map
Version: 0.1.2
Date: 2019-02-23
Author: Marc Fletcher
Maintainer: Marc Fletcher <Marc.Fletcher@hqplantations.com.au>
Description: Performs a fixed radius nearest-neighbour search on a canopy height map with the 
		aim to identify points that are the tallest in their neighbourhood. Parallelism implemented
		with future package.
License: LICENSE
Imports: Rcpp (>= 0.12.18), rgdal (>= 1.3-6), sp (>= 1.3-1), data.table (>= 1.11.8), future (>= 1.10.0)
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo, sp
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
SystemRequirements: C++11
